Head of DEI, Tina Vinod spoke to my classroom of 400+ students in 2020.
This was followed by having Tw LGBTQ+ employees meet students at IIM.
Case studies like Tw’s allow us to present varying progressive and inclusive
perspectives in the classroom. And, the next generation of employees and
managers are the better for it
